As described in your Docs regarding GApps-Integration, you require an ADMIN-Access via API to the GApps-Domain. However, since our Company (3500+ Employees) uses a quite big Installation of which only a fraction of users will use JIRA and which has quite a complicated Sub-Unit structure, we will not grant an Application running outside of our control Admin-Rights.

It appears to me, that you only use that to pull users from GApps, which is not necessary. We'd rather have a simple "Login with Google" like any other site (or better a "Connect with Google" in the profile), that only pulls this user's information on demand.
